dcterms:description: Math23k contains 23,162 Chinese MWPs, which are annotated with equations as their solutions. After cleaning, there are 22,195 MWPs left in Math23k, which is used to evaluate the training method in fully and weakly supervised settings.
dcterms:title: Math23k

dcterms:description: Weak12k is a novel math word problem dataset with 12,117 MWPs, each annotated with a final value answer instead of an equation solution. It is the first Chinese MWP dataset in a weakly supervised manner.
dcterms:title: Weak12k
